{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-strict-equality-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Poredjenje sa Operatorom Stroge Jednakosti","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Stroga jednakost (<code>===</code>) je slicna operatoru jednakosti (<code>==</code>). Medjutim, za razliku od operatora jednakosti koji pokusava da konvertuje obe vrednosti u isti tip, operator stroge jednakosti ne radi konverziju tipa.</p>\n<p>Ako poredjene vrednosti imaju razlicite tipove, smatraju se nejednakim i operator stroge jednakosti vraca false.</p>\n<p><strong>Mifano</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">3 ===  3  // true\n3 === '3' // false\n</code></pre>\n<p>U drugom primeru, <code>3</code> je tipa <code>Number</code>, a <code>'3'</code> tipa <code>String</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d1","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristite operator stroge jednakosti u <code>if</code> iskazu tako da funkcija vraca string <code>Equal</code> kada je <code>val</code> striktno jednako <code>7</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16790,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-strict-equality-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nfunction testStrict(val) {\n  if (val) { // Change this line\n    return \"Equal\";\n  }\n  return \"Not Equal\";\n}\n\ntestStrict(10);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>testStrict(10)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Not Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(testStrict(10) === 'Not Equal');"},{"text":"<p><code>testStrict(7)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(testStrict(7) === 'Equal');"},{"text":"<p><code>testStrict(\"7\")</code> treba da vrati string <code>Not Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(testStrict('7') === 'Not Equal');"},{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite operator <code>===</code></p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/(val\\s*===\\s*\\d+)|(\\d+\\s*===\\s*val)/g).length > 0);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"comparison-with-the-strict-equality-operator","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/practice-comparing-different-values","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-equality-operator","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d1","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-strict-equality-operator"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}